description:
This week, Anna and Sim chat Ed Helms (FATHER FIGURES, THE OFFICE, THE HANGOVER). They reveal their worst talk show experiences (2:45), searching for their identity in school(7:12), then play a round of deal breakers (22:45) and How Would You Proceed? (33:05)

Later they call Julia (51:00) who wants her boyfriend to get to know her family better and needs advice on making that happen. Tune in!
